<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.8.8">
<l>kiḷaroḷiyāṟ kuṟaivillā variyuruvāyk kiḷarnteḻuntu</l>
<l>kiḷaroḷiya viraṇiyaṉa takalmārpaṅ kiḻintukanta</l>
<l>vaḷaroḷiya kaṉalāḻi valampuriyaṉ maṇinīla</l>
<l>vaḷaroḷiyāṉ kavarāta varivaḷaiyāṟ kuṟaivilamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Except the want for [our] intense lustre</l>
<l>we have no want for [our] striped bangles that are not seized by the one of luscious lustre</l>
<l>in sapphire blue, him with the right-spiralling conch, with the lusciously bright glowing discus,</l>
<l>who rejoiced in tearing open the wide chest of intensely bright Hiraṇya,</l>
	<l>emerging [and] rising in lion form.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
